      <name>Sculpture in the City Trail</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Sculpture in the City Trail</b><br><i>Arts &amp; Culture</i><br>Wed 16th Jul – Sat 20th Jun<br>City of London<br>Free<br><br>This summer marks the 14th edition of Sculpture in the City, featuring works by 11 world-class artists across the Square Mile.<br><br><a href="https://londontheinside.com/whats-on-this-week/">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
